CBRE is pleased to offer 97-105 Musgrave Avenue and 28-30 Jimmieson Avenue, Labrador to the market.

This 1.3-hectare*, multi-lot development site is situated in an amenity-rich location that offers developers a substantial development opportunity in a rapidly developing area of the Gold Coast.

The property is uniquely located within an active precinct north-west of the Gold Coast CBD and is within a 2.5-kilometre radius of Harbour Town Shopping Centre, Gold Coast Aquatic Centre, Southport Sharks Entertainment and Sport Facilities, Gold Coast University Hospital and Griffith University.

This site is being offered to the market via an Expressions of Interest campaign closing at 4:00pm, Thursday 16th September 2021.

For further information please contact the exclusive agents listed.
